abilities.name: Tether
abilities.description: Tethers Io to an allied unit, granting bonus movement speed to both. When Io restores health or mana, tethered units target gains a larger portion of that amount. The tether breaks when the allied unit moves too far away, or Io cancels the tether.

abilities.name: Spirits
abilities.description: Summon five particle spirits that dance in a circle around Io. If a particle collides with an enemy hero, it explodes, damaging and slowing all enemy units in an area around it.  Creeps take minor damage from touching a particle spirit, but do not cause them to explode.  When its duration ends, any remaining Spirits explode.

abilities.name: Overcharge
abilities.description: Io gains bonus attack speed and damage reduction.  If Io is Tethered to an ally, that unit also gains the bonuses.

abilities.name: Relocate
abilities.description: Teleports Io and any tethered ally to any location. After the spell expires Io and any tethered ally will return to their original location. Double-click to teleport to your team's base fountain.

abilities.name: Break Tether
abilities.description: Break the link to the tethered unit.

abilities.name: Spirits Movement
abilities.description: Calls the spirits in and out.

talents.name: Tether Grants Scepter Bonus
talents.description: While tethered to a friendly Hero, that Hero gains its Aghanim's Scepter ability upgrades for the duration.

talents.name: Attack Tethered Ally's Target
talents.description: While tethered to a friendly Hero, each time that Hero attacks, Io will attack the same target automatically.
